<h2 style="font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:#12285D;"><span class="mw-headline" id=".C2.A0.C2.A0.C2.A0Selected_picture"><span style="float:left">&#160;<img alt="Featured portal" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/16px-Cscr-featured.svg.png" width="16" height="15" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/24px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/32px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 2x" />&#160;<img alt="Featured portal" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/16px-Cscr-featured.svg.png" width="16" height="15" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/24px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/32px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 2x" />&#160;<img alt="Featured portal" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/16px-Cscr-featured.svg.png" width="16" height="15" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/24px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/32px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 2x" /></span><i>Selected picture</i></span></h2>
</div>
