<div class="plainlinks" style="float:right;margin-bottom:.1em;font-size:80%; color: #12285D"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Portal_American_Civil_War_DYK_05&action=edit.php.html"><span style="color: #12285D">edit</span></a>&#160;&#160;</div>
<h2 style="font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:#12285D;"><span class="mw-headline" id=".C2.A0.C2.A0.C2.A0Did_you_know..."><span style="float:left">&#160;<img alt="Featured portal" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/16px-Cscr-featured.svg.png" width="16" height="15" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/24px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/32px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 2x" />&#160;<img alt="Featured portal" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/16px-Cscr-featured.svg.png" width="16" height="15" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/24px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/32px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 2x" />&#160;<img alt="Featured portal" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/16px-Cscr-featured.svg.png" width="16" height="15" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/24px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e7/Cscr-featured.svg/32px-Cscr-featured.svg.png 2x" /></span><i>Did you know...</i></span></h2>
</div>
<div style="border: 1px solid #A2A2A2; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: #F5F5F5;opacity: 1; color: #000000; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">
<ul>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">... that <a href="Kasim_Reed" title="Kasim Reed">Kasim Reed</a>, a 2009 <a href="Atlanta_mayor" title="Atlanta mayor" class="mw-redirect">Atlanta mayoral</a> candidate, is known for keeping the battle emblem of the <a href="Confederate_States_of_America" title="Confederate States of America">Confederate States of America</a> from being considered for inclusion on the <a href="../Flag_of_Georgia_(U.S._state)" title="Flag of Georgia (U.S. state)">Georgia State Flag</a>?</li>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">... that <a href="French_weapons_in_the_American_Civil_War" title="French weapons in the American Civil War">French-designed cannons</a>, manufactured in both the <a href="Union_(American_Civil_War)" title="Union (American Civil War)">North</a> and the <a href="Confederate_States_of_America" title="Confederate States of America">South</a>, were the primary <a href="Artillery" title="Artillery">artillery</a> weapons of the <a href="American_Civil_War" title="American Civil War">American Civil War</a>?</li>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">... that <a href="../Henry_C._Wayne" title="Henry C. Wayne">Confederate General Henry C. Wayne</a> gained a <i>First Class Medal of Mammal Division by the Société impériale zoologique d'acclimatation</i> for his introduction of the <a href="Camel" title="Camel">camel</a> to the <a href="United_States" title="United States">United States</a>?</li>
<li style="-moz-float-edge: content-box">... that <a href="Charles_Thomas_Campbell" title="Charles Thomas Campbell">Charles Thomas Campbell</a>, who served as a <a href="Union_Army" title="Union Army">Union Army</a> <a href="General_officer" title="General officer">general</a>, helped found the town of <a href="Scotland,_South_Dakota" title="Scotland, South Dakota">Scotland, South Dakota</a>?
<div class="noprint" style="text-align:right; margin:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em; padding:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em;"><b><a href="Did_you_know/Archive1/index.html" title="Portal:American Civil War/Did you know/Archive1">Archive</a> • <a href="Did_you_know/index.html" title="Portal:American Civil War/Did you know">Create</a> • <a href="Did_you_know/Suggest/index.html" title="Portal:American Civil War/Did you know/Suggest">Suggest</a> • <a href="Portal_talk_American_Civil_War/Did_you_know" title="Portal talk:American Civil War/Did you know">Talk</a></b></div>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
