rbes" title="Edwin Forbes">Edwin Forbes</a> • <a href="../Hiram_B._Granbury" title="Hiram B. Granbury">Hiram B. Granbury</a> • <a href="Henry_Thomas_Harrison" title="Henry Thomas Harrison">Henry Thomas Harrison</a> • <a href="Ben_Hardin_Helm" title="Ben Hardin Helm" class="mw-redirect">Ben Hardin Helm</a> • <a href="Louis_H%C3%A9bert_(colonel)" title="Louis Hébert (colonel)" class="mw-redirect">Louis Hébert (colonel)</a> • <a href="../Benjamin_G._Humphreys" title="Benjamin G. Humphreys">Benjamin G. Humphreys</a> • <a href="../Lunsford_L._Lomax" title="Lunsford L. Lomax">Lunsford L. Lomax</a> • <a href="Maynard_Carbine" title="Maynard Carbine" class="mw-redirect">Maynard Carbine</a> • <a href="Daniel_Ruggles" title="Daniel Ruggles">Daniel Ruggles</a> • <a href="../Thomas_W._Sherman" title="Thomas W. Sherman">Thomas W. Sherman</a> • <a href="../Hezekiah_G._Spruill" title="Hezekiah G. Spruill">Hezekiah G. Spruill</a> • <a href="Smith_Percussion_Carbine" title="Smith Percussion Carbine" class="mw-redirect">Smith Percussion Carbine</a> • <a href="../Edward_C._Walthall" title="Edward C. Walthall">Edward C. Walthall</a> • <a href="Confederate_States_Secretary_of_the_Navy" title="Confederate States Secretary of the Navy">Confederate States Secretary of the Navy</a> • <a href="Confederate_States_Secretary_of_the_Treasury" title="Confederate States Secretary of the Treasury" class="mw-redirect">Confederate States Secretary of the Treasury</a> • <a href="Delaware_in_the_American_Civil_War" title="Delaware in the American Civil War" class="mw-redirect">Delaware in the American Civil War</a> • <a href="Ironclad_Board" title="Ironclad Board">Ironclad Board</a> • <a href="United_States_Military_Railroad" title="United States Military Railroad">United States Military Railroad</a> • <a href="Category_American_Civil_War_battle_stubs" title="Category:American Civil War battle stubs"><i>Other American Civil War battle stubs</i></a> • <a href="Category_American_Civil_War_stubs" title="Category:American Civil War stubs"><i>Other American Civil War stubs</i></a><br />
